---
import Layout from "../Layouts/layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div id="body-wrapper">
    <section class="header-bg"></section>
    <div id="terms-and-privacy">
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Privacy Statement</h1>
        <p>
          At The Serious Sandwich, we're passionate about serving up delicious
          sandwiches and fries, and we're just as passionate about protecting
          your privacy.
        </p>

        <h2>What Information Do We Collect?</h2>
        <p>
          When you visit our website or order from us, we might collect some
          information from you, like:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your name and contact details</li>
          <li>Your order history and preferences</li>
          <li>
            Your payment information (don't worry, we keep this safe and
            secure!)
          </li>
          <li>Some technical stuff like your IP address and browser type</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How Do We Use Your Information?</h2>
        <p>We use your information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Make sure your orders are processed smoothly and efficiently</li>
          <li>
            Keep you in the loop about new menu items, promotions, and events
          </li>
          <li>
            Improve our website and services to make them more user-friendly and
            awesome
          </li>
          <li>Keep your personal info safe and secure</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How Do We Keep Your Information Safe?</h2>
        <p>
          We take security seriously! We use encryption, firewalls, and access
          controls to keep your info safe from prying eyes.
        </p>

        <h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
        <p>We might share your info with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Our affiliates and subsidiaries (they're like our sandwich-loving
            family!)
          </li>
          <li>
            Our service providers (like payment processors and delivery
            companies)
          </li>
          <li>
            Law enforcement agencies or regulatory authorities (if we're
            required to by law)
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under the New Zealand Privacy Act 2020, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access your personal info</li>
          <li>Correct any errors or inaccuracies</li>
          <li>
            Delete your personal info (although we'll be sad to see you go!)
          </li>
          <li>
            Opt-out of receiving marketing materials (we promise we won't spam
            you!)
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Changes to This Privacy Statement</h2>
        <p>
          We might update this privacy statement from time to time. If we do,
          we'll post the updated version on our website.
        </p>

        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy statement,
          please don't hesitate to contact us via the 'Contact Us' function on
          this website.
        </p>

        <p>
          Thanks for choosing The Serious Sandwich! We're stoked to have you as
          part of our sandwich-loving community!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
